                      "text": "Genius Invokation TCG Stage",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tantangan Tavern: Persahabatan - Bisikan Electro Hypostasis",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Pengenalan Stage",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meong.\" \"Indra kami sangat tajam. Ketika ada bahaya, 'suara'-nya saja bisa kedengaran. Itulah kenapa semua kucing menghindari makhluk kubus warna ungu itu!\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Aturan Khusus: Electro Hypostasis kebal terhadap Frozen, Stun, serta Petrification, dan akan memulai duel dengan mengenakan \"Elemental Lifeform: Electro\" yang dapat memulihkan hingga 6 poin HP saat memicu Electro Crystal Core;",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 153, 153)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Maksimum terpicu 2 kali pada saat Tahap Aksi dimulai: Jika Electro Hypostasis tidak memiliki Electro Crystal Core, ia dapat mengenakan Electro Crystal Core-nya kembali.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Lineup Lawan",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3844,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/19/25750596/a18a61786bc99b67ad9fde145786cbe3_6337201424625501576.png",
                      "menu_id": 17,
                      "name": "Electro Hypostasis",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "*Memiliki 30 HP",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Prasyarat",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Pemain harus mencapai Lv.8",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Target Tantangan",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
